<lb ed="I" n="0082a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>大魏故昭玄沙門大統令法師墓誌銘</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
