<lb ed="I" n="0082a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0082a0101">大魏故昭
<lb ed="I" n="0082a02" type="honorific"/>玄沙門大
<lb ed="I" n="0082a03" type="honorific"/>統令法師
<lb ed="I" n="0082a04" type="honorific"/>之墓誌銘</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0082b00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">銘</cb:mulu><head>銘</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0082b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0082b0101">魏故昭玄沙門大統僧令法師墓誌銘
<lb ed="I" n="0082b02" type="honorific"/>法師緣姓杜。京兆人也。幼而<note n="0082001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">慜＝敏【史】</note><app n="0082001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">敏</lem><rdg wit="【原】">慜</rdg></app>惠。志尚清<note n="0082002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30579"/>＝虛【史】</note><app n="0082002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30579"/></rdg></app>。爰在兒童。脫
<lb ed="I" n="0082b03" type="honorific"/>俗歸道。學既多聞。善亦兼濟。散<note n="0082003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧙍＝袟【史】</note><app n="0082003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">袟</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧙍</rdg></app>濡翰。怡然自<note n="0082004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">淂＝得【史】</note><app n="0082004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">得</lem><rdg wit="【原】">淂</rdg></app>。若其涉
<lb ed="I" n="0082b04" type="honorific"/><note n="0082005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">獦＝獵【史】</note><app n="0082005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">獵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">獦</rdg></app>群品。富同河漢。討論微<note n="0082006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30580"/>＝賾【史】</note><app n="0082006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">賾</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30580"/></rdg></app>。殆剖秋豪。良以三空靡遺。九
<lb ed="I" n="0082b05" type="honorific"/>典咸<note n="0082007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨖫＝達【史】</note><app n="0082007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">達</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨖫</rdg></app>。居室遐應。鳴<note n="0082008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">睪＝皋【史】</note><app n="0082008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">皋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">睪</rdg></app>自遠。高祖光宅土中。憲章大備。存
<lb ed="I" n="0082b06" type="honorific"/>心釋氏。注意法輪。由此聞風<note n="0082009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣣽＝欽【史】</note><app n="0082009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">欽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣣽</rdg></app>想。發於寤寐。嘉命苹心。荷
<lb ed="I" n="0082b07" type="honorific"/><note n="0082010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30582"/>＝錫【史】</note><app n="0082010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">錫</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30582"/></rdg></app>來遊。至若振塵式<note n="0082011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">乹＝乾【史】</note><app n="0082011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">乾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">乹</rdg></app>。洞窮幽<note n="0082012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣅀＝旨【史】</note><app n="0082012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣅀</rdg></app>。故以造<note n="0082013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦡀＝膝【史】</note><app n="0082013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">膝</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦡀</rdg></app>嗟善。徘徊定
<lb ed="I" n="0082b08" type="honorific"/>倦。武明之世。<note n="0082014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">礼＝禮【史】</note><app n="0082014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">礼</rdg></app>遇彌隆。乃以法師為嵩高閑居寺主。飲泉
<lb ed="I" n="0082b09" type="honorific"/>庇樹。嘯想煙霞。一丘一壑。<app type="star" corresp="#0082004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">得</lem><rdg wit="【原】">淂</rdg></app>之懷抱。實有高蹈之志。非無
<lb ed="I" n="0082b10" type="honorific"/>遂往之情。雖跡出塵中。而尚羈世綱。尋被徵為沙門都維
<lb ed="I" n="0082b11" type="honorific"/>那。屢自陳遜。終不見許。既弗獲以<app type="star" corresp="#0082014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">禮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">礼</rdg></app>。便同之畏法。莊帝聿
<lb ed="I" n="0082b12" type="honorific"/>興。<note n="0082015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30583"/>＝仍【史】</note><app n="0082015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">仍</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30583"/></rdg></app>轉為統。自居斯任。彌<note n="0082016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">厯＝歷【史】</note><app n="0082016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">厯</rdg></app>數朝。事無蹔壅。眾咸歸德。今
<lb ed="I" n="0082b13" type="honorific"/>上龍飛。固乞收退。頻煩切至。久而方允。於是隱輪養志。保
<lb ed="I" n="0082b14" type="honorific"/>素任真。形影雖<note n="0082017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𤱊＝留【史】</note><app n="0082017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">留</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𤱊</rdg></app>。心神已化。俄遘篤疾。奄然<note n="0082018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">辞＝辭【史】</note><app n="0082018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">辞</rdg></app>世。行年八
<lb ed="I" n="0082b15" type="honorific"/>十有一。臨終自<app type="star" corresp="#0082004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">得</lem><rdg wit="【原】">淂</rdg></app>。安然若歸。天子追悼。敕主書任元景詣
<lb ed="I" n="0082b16" type="honorific"/>寺宣慰。二月三日丙辰。窆於芒山之陽。弟子智微。道遜。覺
<lb ed="I" n="0082b17" type="honorific"/>意等。<note n="0082019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30415"/>＝痛【史】</note><app n="0082019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">痛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30415"/></rdg></app>慈顏之長往。懼大義之將乖。興言永慕。乃作銘曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0082b18" type="honorific"/>天生英德。志逸旻穹。孤拔塵表。獨<app type="star" corresp="#0082004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">得</lem><rdg wit="【原】">淂</rdg></app>環中。道与物合。行共
<lb ed="I" n="0082b19" type="honorific"/>時融。百代飛譽。千載垂風。道逸繢<note n="0082020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨓍＝庭【史】</note><app n="0082020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">庭</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨓍</rdg></app>聲飛未<note n="0082021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨷂＝闕【史】</note><app n="0082021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">闕</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨷂</rdg></app>。見重高帝。
<lb ed="I" n="0082b20" type="honorific"/>尺書屢發。雅論移天。清談動月。其人雖往。斯音未歇。
<lb ed="I" n="0082b21" type="honorific"/>　大魏永熙三年歲次甲寅二月甲寅<note n="0082022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦙚＝朔【史】</note><app n="0082022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦙚</rdg></app>三日丙辰</p>
